Results.ReviewText: Love Azera, it really is the closest you can get to proper barista coffee. When I'm not feeling extra lazy, I even choose it above my Dolce Gusto machine! These packs are even more awesome, as not only do you just have to add hot water, they come with an extremely handy closable lid - perfect for the clumsy people like me! :) I also like the quirky phrases on the cups, they bring a smile to my face. A well thought out product, kudos Nescafe! :)
